Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.57,0:00:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Akil. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.32,0:00:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was 18, \Nmy family moved to a new city. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.99,0:00:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It was bad enough \Nleaving my friends behind. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.40,0:00:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.00,0:00:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn’t sure \Nif I could make new ones.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.78,0:00:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My parents seemed really happy. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.20,0:00:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn’t want \Nto make them feel bad \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.97,0:00:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,by telling them how I really felt.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.78,0:00:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The new school \Nwasn’t much better \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.30,0:00:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,until I met Cameron. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.43,0:00:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He seemed \Nlike a pretty cool guy. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.58,0:01:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon, his friends \Nbecame my friends.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.12,0:01:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,. . . something that David \Nbelieved was true, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.13,0:01:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,he actually proved it \Nby the association that he kept.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.87,0:01:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We think about one \Nof the closest friendships \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.93,0:01:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,recorded in the Scriptures, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.47,0:01:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and it was \Nthat of David and Jonathan. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.98,0:01:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it that David and Jonathan \Nshared in common? \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.19,0:01:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn’t their age.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.69,0:01:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Akil, \Nyou were texting in the meeting.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.86,0:01:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn’t have sent the text. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.11,0:01:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.76,0:01:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But Cameron is a good person. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.16,0:01:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He might even study one day.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.74,0:01:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that, Akil. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.33,0:01:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But we all have to be careful \Nwith how much time \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.30,0:01:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,we spend with people \Nthat don’t love Jehovah. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.79,0:01:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,See, \Ntheir values are just different. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You know \Nwhat Proverbs 13:20 says: \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.13,0:01:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,‘Walk with those who are wise.’ \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So why don’t you seek out \Nfriends who love Jehovah? \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.22,0:01:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And you will make friends \Nthat last a lifetime.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.10,0:01:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to do that? \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.60,0:02:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s no one my age \Nin the congregation.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.14,0:02:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Akil, good friends \Ncan come from unexpected places.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.90,0:02:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, \NI had good friends\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.57,0:02:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,—back home.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.70,0:02:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We all felt bad that night.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.71,0:02:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The next day, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.80,0:02:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Cameron posted pictures \Nof a party he had. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My parents were right. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.35,0:02:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I broke off my association \Nwith Cameron \N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.52,0:02:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and his friends, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.39,0:02:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,but I still felt \N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.39,0:02:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,lost.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.41,0:02:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Akil? \N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have \Nfield service plans for Saturday?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.87,0:02:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, no.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.63,0:02:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. \NNow you do. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:02:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll see you \Nat the 9:30 a.m. meeting, OK?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.97,0:03:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,After service, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.43,0:03:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Max had the group \Nover for refreshments.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you take these?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.94,0:03:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like them?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.15,0:03:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,My wife, \Nshe was always the photographer. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She loved photography. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.78,0:03:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And then one anniversary \Nshe went out and bought me a camera, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and from that moment on, \NI was hooked too.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.79,0:03:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Time flies so quickly. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s hard to believe \Nshe passed away 12 years ago now.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.50,0:03:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s OK.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But you still take pictures?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.88,0:03:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I do. \NI really enjoy photography. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.65,0:03:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s something about being close \N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.67,0:04:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,to Jehovah’s creation. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It reminds me \N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.33,0:04:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that we’re never really alone, \Nyou know?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.47,0:04:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Good friends can come \Nfrom unexpected places \N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and unexpected ages. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.32,0:04:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,As I spent more time with Max, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.95,0:04:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized it was \Njust like David and Jonathan. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.60,0:04:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Their friendship was based, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,not on age, \Nbut on their love for Jehovah. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.72,0:04:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And they helped each other.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.04,0:04:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And with Max’s help, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I was able to keep \Na good spiritual routine \N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.26,0:04:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,without interruption. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.27,0:04:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Although we weren’t the same age, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.77,0:04:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Max became my good friend. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.78,0:04:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I just needed to see \Nwhat was right \N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.99,0:05:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,in front of me.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.94,0:00:09.70,Default2,,0,0,0,,名前はアキル\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.70,0:00:13.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,18の時 家族で引っ越した\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.54,0:00:18.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,友達と別れるのは辛かった\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.04,0:00:24.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,それに 新しくできるかも分からない\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.47,0:00:30.97,Default2,,0,0,0,,両親はとても幸せそう\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.97,0:00:33.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,だから心配をかけたくない\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.10,0:00:39.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,僕の気持ちを話すと\Nがっかりするだろうから\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.35,0:00:44.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,学校は退屈だった\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.78,0:00:51.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,キャメロンに会うまでは\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:55.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,いい奴そうだな\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.16,0:01:03.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,すぐに 友達が増えた\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.13,0:01:09.76,Default2,,0,0,0,,…ダビデの信頼は心からのもので—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.76,0:01:13.39,Default2,,0,0,0,,彼が保った友情がそれを証ししています\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.39,0:01:15.68,Default2,,0,0,0,,ダビデとヨナタンの友情関係について—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.68,0:01:17.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,聖書から考えてみましょう\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.10,0:01:24.10,Default2,,0,0,0,,2人の友情は何に基づいていましたか？\N年齢でしょうか？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.10,0:01:27.23,Default2,,0,0,0,,アキル 集会中メールしてたわね\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.23,0:01:30.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,分かってる ごめん\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.74,0:01:34.66,Default2,,0,0,0,,でも キャメロンはいい奴なんだ\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.66,0:01:36.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,いつか研究するかも\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.12,0:01:38.87,Default2,,0,0,0,,気持ちは分かるよ\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.87,0:01:44.79,Default2,,0,0,0,,でも エホバを愛さない人と\Nいつも一緒にいることには注意しないと\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.79,0:01:46.96,Default2,,0,0,0,,持ってる基準が違うね\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.96,0:01:51.97,Default2,,0,0,0,,箴言 13章20節が言うように\N“賢い者たちと共に歩”むんだ\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.97,0:01:54.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,エホバを愛する友達を探してごらん\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.14,0:01:57.51,Default2,,0,0,0,,ずっと続く友達が見つかるよ\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.51,0:02:01.68,Default2,,0,0,0,,どうやってできるの？\N会衆に同い年なんていないよ\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.68,0:02:05.19,Default2,,0,0,0,,親友は思いがけないところにいるものよ\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.19,0:02:08.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,親友は…いたよ\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.07,0:02:11.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,前にね\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.91,0:02:18.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,その夜はたくさん話し合った\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.67,0:02:32.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,次の日 キャメロンが\Nパーティーの写真を見せてくれた\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.47,0:02:37.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,両親は正しかった\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.85,0:02:41.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,キャメロン達と付き合うのはやめた\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.68,0:02:47.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,でも また独りぼっちだ\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.69,0:02:53.19,Default2,,0,0,0,,アキル\N土曜日だれかと奉仕する？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.19,0:02:54.53,Default2,,0,0,0,,ああ いえ\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.53,0:02:58.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,そう なら9時半に集合場所で\Nいいかい？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:22.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,奉仕の後\Nマックス兄弟が家に招いてくれた\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:27.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,兄弟これ……？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:29.27,Default2,,0,0,0,,気に入った？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:30.56,Default2,,0,0,0,,ええ\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:33.23,Default2,,0,0,0,,妻が いつもカメラ持って—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:35.24,Default2,,0,0,0,,熱中していたんだ\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.24,0:03:38.66,Default2,,0,0,0,,で 結婚記念日に カメラをくれたんだ\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.66,0:03:41.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,それから わたしもとりこだよ\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:44.79,Default2,,0,0,0,,ほんとに早い\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.79,0:03:48.71,Default2,,0,0,0,,妻が亡くなってもう\N12年も過ぎたとはね\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.71,0:03:49.79,Default2,,0,0,0,,そうですね\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:50.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,まあね\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.17,0:03:53.59,Default2,,0,0,0,,でも…今でも写真を？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.59,0:03:56.76,Default2,,0,0,0,,ああ\N撮るのは楽しいよ\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.76,0:03:59.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,特に相手は エホバの創造物だ\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.64,0:04:02.18,Default2,,0,0,0,,そんな時—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:05.31,Default2,,0,0,0,,独りぼっちじゃないって感じるんだ\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.31,0:04:06.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,どう？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:14.82,Default2,,0,0,0,,親友は思いがけないところにいる\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.82,0:04:16.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,年が違っても\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:21.82,Default2,,0,0,0,,兄弟と知り合うにつれて 分かったんだ\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:24.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,ダビデとヨナタンみたいだ\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.58,0:04:27.66,Default2,,0,0,0,,2人の友情の基盤は—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.66,0:04:31.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,年齢じゃなく エホバへの愛だった\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:35.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,そしてお互いに支え合った\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.76,0:04:42.34,Default2,,0,0,0,,マックス兄弟の助けで—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:46.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,今も良い霊的な習慣を\N続けることができている\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:51.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,年が違っても 兄弟と親友になれた\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.73,0:04:54.73,Default2,,0,0,0,,目を向ければよかったんだ\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:05:06.52,Default2,,0,0,0,,目の前にある正しいことに\N
